{"type":null,"faqId":20884,"title":"发送彩信","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>进入信息菜单，点击</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=70016\" style=\"width:0.4340278in;height:0.33958334in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>，撰写新信息；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>输入收件人和编辑消息内容；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3.  </span><span>点击文本框左边</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=70017\" style=\"width:0.375in;height:0.33333334in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>，再选择</span><span class=\"s2\">添加主题</span><span>（添加主题后自动转换为彩信）；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4.  </span><span>点击文本框左边</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=70018\" style=\"width:0.375in;height:0.33333334in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>按钮添加附件，可以加入图片、音频或视频（添加多媒体文件自动转成彩信）；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">5.  </span><span>编辑完成后，点击</span><span class=\"s2\">发送</span><span>。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=70019\" style=\"width:1.8673611in;height:3.3194444in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=70020\" style=\"width:1.8673611in;height:3.3194444in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4547","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1426837622000,"seriesProductName":"Pine-CL00,Pine-CL10,Pine-TL00M,Pine-TL10,Pine-TL20,Pine-UL00","visitedTimes":13,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}